  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1039">
<l>cellāṉ kiḻava ṉiruppi ṉilampulan</l>
<l>tillāḷi ṉūṭi viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the owner does not (personally) attend to his cultivation, his land will behave like an angry wife and yield him no pleasure.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
